# Copy to scrapers/.env (gitignored — this repo is public, real credentials never go in it)
# and fill in. Used only by `tb enrich-ariba-attachments --capture` (#117) to log the headed
# browser into a SAP Ariba supplier account so the Respond gate opens. Respond registers our
# account as an event participant for archival access (authorized by PMMD); a bid is never
# submitted. The account must not have MFA/2FA — an unattended login cannot answer a challenge.
ARIBA_USERNAME=your-ariba-supplier-username
ARIBA_PASSWORD=your-ariba-supplier-password
